<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 12:13:48 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>对以色列战争撤离人员的资助即将到期；政府尚未决定继续提供资金</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-04/ty-article/.premium/funding-for-israeli-war-evacuees-set-to-expire-govt-yet-to-decide-on-continued-funds/00000190-7d5c-d835-a9fb-ffffde960000</link><description>财政部批准为北部流离失所的居民提供资金直至 7 月 7 日，在接到指示与真主党的冲突将于该日期结束后，寻求额外资金的努力引发了激烈的政治争论</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 11:50:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-04/ty-article/.premium/funding-for-israeli-war-evacuees-set-to-expire-govt-yet-to-decide-on-continued-funds/00000190-7d5c-d835-a9fb-ffffde960000</guid></item><item><title>以色列人真的想与真主党发生全面战争吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-04/ty-article/.premium/do-israelis-really-want-full-scale-war-with-hezbollah/00000190-7d43-d5c3-a596-7d4f39800000</link><description>“我们只是在等待战争。”在街头和媒体上，以色列人似乎相信，与黎巴嫩真主党的全面战争即将来临。但民意调查显示公众意见存在分歧，生活在重大冲突前线的以色列北部的公众人物提出了发人深省的评估</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 11:16:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-04/ty-article/.premium/do-israelis-really-want-full-scale-war-with-hezbollah/00000190-7d43-d5c3-a596-7d4f39800000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡授予外交部长特别许可，允许其携带妻子参加所有由政府承担费用的海外旅行</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-04/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-grants-fm-permission-to-bring-wife-on-all-overseas-travel-at-govt-expense/00000190-7d0a-d0b6-a9b1-7dfea3490000</link><description>外交部长获得了不同寻常的全面批准，可以与妻子一起旅行，费用由政府承担。一位外交消息人士称，“在这样的时刻，这是不必要的、令人愤慨的浪费金钱”</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 10:48:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-04/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-grants-fm-permission-to-bring-wife-on-all-overseas-travel-at-govt-expense/00000190-7d0a-d0b6-a9b1-7dfea3490000</guid></item><item><title>本古里安机场预计夏季旅客人数激增，但仍低于战前水平</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-04/ty-article/.premium/ben-gurion-airport-expects-summer-surge-in-passengers-still-below-pre-war-levels/00000190-7d33-d835-a9fb-ffbb2c030000</link><description>以色列机场管理局预计 7 月和 8 月将有 180 万名旅客乘飞机出行，而去年分别为 260 万人次和 290 万人次</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 10:30:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-04/ty-article/.premium/ben-gurion-airport-expects-summer-surge-in-passengers-still-below-pre-war-levels/00000190-7d33-d835-a9fb-ffbb2c030000</guid></item><item><title>“一些法国犹太人会接受议会中的极右反犹太主义，因为他们相信勒庞会保护他们”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2024-07-04/ty-article-podcast/some-french-jews-believe-le-pen-will-protect-them/00000190-78c9-d7ff-a7b2-fbfb880b0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 09:53:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2024-07-04/ty-article-podcast/some-french-jews-believe-le-pen-will-protect-them/00000190-78c9-d7ff-a7b2-fbfb880b0000</guid></item><item><title>由于争论持续存在，哈马斯对以色列提议的回应令消息人士持“乐观”态度</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-04/ty-article/.premium/sources-optimistic-following-hamas-response-to-israeli-proposal-as-contentions-persist/00000190-7caa-d835-a9fb-ffbbad090000</link><description>一位以色列外交消息人士称，哈马斯并不坚持“全面停火”。另一位人士表示，内塔尼亚胡发布了一份官方声明，称该组织坚持停火和从加沙撤军是“不可接受的”</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 09:33:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-04/ty-article/.premium/sources-optimistic-following-hamas-response-to-israeli-proposal-as-contentions-persist/00000190-7caa-d835-a9fb-ffbbad090000</guid></item><item><title>本尼·莫里斯如何学会停止担忧并热爱炸弹</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-07-04/ty-article/.