">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-04/ty-article-live/hamas-positive-on-cease-fire-talks-israeli-source-basis-for-progress/00000190-7b75-d5c3-a596-7f7fde080000</guid></item><item><title>新调查驳斥以色列最初调查：1982年轮胎灾难是恐怖袭击，不是瓦斯爆炸</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-04/ty-article/.premium/new-inquiry-refutes-original-israeli-probe-1982-tyre-disaster-was-terror-not-gas-blast/00000190-7a17-d3cb-a7ff-fb7fe05a0000</link><description>黎巴嫩城市 91 人被杀四十多年后，一项新的调查证实了许多人的怀疑：这起真主党首次自杀式袭击是由一名什叶派恐怖分子驾驶一辆装满炸药的汽车发动的</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 21:28:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-04/ty-article/.premium/new-inquiry-refutes-original-israeli-probe-1982-tyre-disaster-was-terror-not-gas-blast/00000190-7a17-d3cb-a7ff-fb7fe05a0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡不想“回到 10 月 6 日”，这是有充分理由的</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-03/ty-article-opinion/.premium/netanyahu-doesnt-want-to-go-back-to-october-6-and-for-a-good-reason/00000190-7994-d5c3-a596-7ddeb6b70000</link><description></description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 20:51:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-03/ty-article-opinion/.premium/netanyahu-doesnt-want-to-go-back-to-october-6-and-for-a-good-reason/00000190-7994-d5c3-a596-7ddeb6b70000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军官在加沙战斗中丧生，三名士兵受伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-03/ty-article/israeli-soldier-killed-in-gaza-strip-fighting-idf-announces/00000190-7a39-d835-a9fb-fbbb995d0000</link><description>周三，Elay Elisha Lugasi 上尉在 Shujaiyeh 被反坦克导弹击中身亡</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 20:24:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-03/ty-article/israeli-soldier-killed-in-gaza-strip-fighting-idf-announces/00000190-7a39-d835-a9fb-fbbb995d0000</guid></item><item><title>两名以色列科学家荣获 2024 年沃尔夫奖</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-03/ty-article/.premium/two-israeli-scientists-among-this-years-wolf-prize-winners/00000190-79d9-dbb2-a3f0-fddb55790000</link><description>其他获奖者包括英国物理学教授马丁·里斯（Martin Rees）； Botond Roska 和 Jose-Alain Sahel 在医学领域；三位美国农业教授——埃利奥特·迈耶罗维茨 (Elliot Meyerowitz)、乔安妮·乔里 (Joanne Chory) 和文卡特桑·桑达雷桑 (Venkatesan Sundaresan) 教授；和匈牙利作曲家乔治·库塔格（Gyorgy Kurtag）的音乐</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 19:31:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-03/ty-article/.premium/two-israeli-scientists-among-this-years-wolf-prize-winners/00000190-79d9-dbb2-a3f0-fddb55790000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡的噩梦：以色列国防军和拜登政府联手对付他</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-03/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-nightmare-the-idf-and-the-biden-administration-ganging-up-against-him/00000190-79c1-d0b6-a9b1-7df5debb0000</link><description>以色列总理对以色列国防军支持加沙停火的报道的回应突显了他对受到军方和拜登政府破坏的担忧，因为对弹药和真主党潜在升级的担忧日益凸显</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 19:19:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-03/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-nightmare-the-idf-and-the-biden-administration-ganging-up-against-him/00000190-79c1-d0b6-a9b1-7df5debb0000</guid></item><item><title>禁止未经审判拘留犹太人的法案在议会通过了第一个障碍</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-03/ty-article/.premium/bill-to-bar-detention-without-trial-for-jews-passes-first-hurdle-in-knesset/00000190-79b5-d37b-a59c-fdb7e0fc0000</link><description>该立法旨在加大对犹太定居者进行“行政拘留”或未经审判的拘留的难度</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 18:24:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-03/ty-article/.premium/bill-to-bar-detention-without-trial-for-jews-passes-first-hurdle-in-knesset/00000190-79b5-d37b-a59c-fdb7e0fc0000</guid></item><item><title>拜登为内塔尼亚胡铺红地毯是不可原谅的</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-07-03/ty-article/.highlight/for-biden-to-roll-out-the-red-carpet-for-netanyahu-is-inexcusable/00000190-792d-d37b-a59c-fdbfb7040000</link><description>拜登面临着证明他的认知